let container = {
  overflowY: "scroll",
  overflowX: "hidden",
  position: "absolute", 
  width: "33vw", 
  height: "85.5vh", 
  left: "65.5vw",
  top: "13vh"
}

let focusedItem = {
  width: "calc(33vw - 17px)", 
  height: "25px",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  color: "white",
  fontSize: "17px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px"
}

let focusedItemDD = {
  width: "calc(33vw - 19px)", 
  height: "316px",
  borderWidth: "0px 1px 1px 1px",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  marginBottom: "5px"
}

export {
  container,
  focusedItem,
  focusedItemDD
}
